# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# The aliens prototype lives at /aliens/ (a directory index). Pages resolves /aliens -> /aliens/
# natively; these catch the variants people actually type: the singular "alien" and the
# capital-first forms a phone keyboard autocapitalizes to. Without these, the missing path
# falls through to the SPA shell and shows the panda game instead of the alien prototype.
/alien     /aliens/   301
/alien/    /aliens/   301
/Alien     /aliens/   301
/Alien/    /aliens/   301
/Aliens*   /aliens/   301
/ALIENS*   /aliens/   301
# Space Force Kitties lives at /kitties/ — catch the singular + autocapitalized variants.
/kitty     /kitties/   301
/kitty/    /kitties/   301
/Kitty     /kitties/   301
/Kitty/    /kitties/   301
/Kitties*  /kitties/   301
/KITTIES*  /kitties/   301
# Game of Kitties (knights saga) lives at /knights/ — catch singular + autocapitalized variants.
/knight     /knights/   301
/knight/    /knights/   301
/Knight     /knights/   301
/Knight/    /knights/   301
/Knights*   /knights/   301
/KNIGHTS*   /knights/   301
